data.description: Nestled in a prime location on a vibrant street, this two-story house offers a versatile and dynamic space suitable for both residential and commercial purposes. With a separate entrance, clients or customers can easily access the commercial unit without disturbing the residential space.  The house boasts 3 nicely sized bedrooms that feature ample closet space to accommodate your storage needs. There are two full bathrooms and two half bathrooms. There’s a beautifully appointed living space that offers a cozy and private oasis. Large windows allow natural light to flood the space, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The kitchen is thoughtfully designed, combining functionality and style. It features modern appliances, ample counter space, and storage options. The property also includes a fenced backyard which can be used for relaxation, gardening, or as an additional amenity for tenants.   This property provides excellent income potential due to its dual-use design. The options to rent out the ground floor commercial unit or to rent out the residential space and utilize the ground floor for your own business endeavors. Whether you choose to live and work here or lease out both units, this property provides endless possibilities for a fulfilling and profitable lifestyle!
